                    <hotlnk xrefid="f9803031">figure 1</hotlnk>.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Installer les ressorts &#224; 2 phases, num&#233;ro de pi&#232;ce 3521859C91 (
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f9803032">figure 2</hotlnk>).
                </para>
            </step1>
